fields.description:
This is a little bit of information about me! Good to have you here looking at my profile. As you will see there is work to be done in making it look better.

I am a Project Manager in Events Management and I am looking forward to meeting you at one of the meetups!

Hi everyone, I am a community manager on this site, as well as an Event Manager in the real world. Keen to meet many of you on here from and expand my network of freelancers! 

You can contact us using the link in the footer if you have any issues during your time on the site, otherwise I look forward to meeting you soon!

fields.title: Evening Cocktails for Film & TV Freelancers!
fields.description:
As the industry starts to pick up again, we thought it would be about time we gathered our fellow freelance friends to reminisce on old projects and discuss what's new! 

Expand your network and enjoy a free Margherita or two!

fields.title: Event Producer Meetup
fields.description:
Hello fellow Producers in the live events world! About time we had a little get together to catch up on lost time, build new connections and help each other secure more projects.

Looking forward to meeting you all!
